OL,7,Fairs on BBC One. It's held in
OL,8,FHarrogate, North Yorkshire. The show is
OL,9,Fpresented by Jan Leeming, with Terry
OL,10,FWogan on commentary. Bardo (the group
OL,11,Fincluded Sally Ann Triplett) was 7th
OL,12,Ffor the UK. Nicole from West Germany
OL,13,Fwon.
